UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 983
1 the Governor in making tours of inspection, mustering in or mustering out
2 troops, making surveys of military property, sitting on courts-martial,
3 summary courts, efficiency boards, courts of inquiry or boards of officers, or
4 performance of any other duty directed by the Governor or adjutant general;
5 (c) The participation of any unit or units of the Kentucky National Guard in
6 gunnery competition or other training or military exercise anywhere within or
7 without the United States.
8 (5) Words importing the masculine gender only shall extend to and be applied to
9 females as well as males.
